<div class="mw-parser-output">
 <p>
  <br/>
  Operations Bridge can use NFS or Amazon Elastic File System (EFS) as its shared storage solution. The EFS service is not available in all AWS regions. Make sure to select an AWS region with EFS support if you plan to use EFS. The suite deployment may fail if a region without EFS support is selected.
 </p>
 <p>
  For the latest information and list of AWS regions that support EFS, refer to the following Amazon website:
  <br/>
  <a class="external text" href="https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/global-infrastructure/regional-product-services/" rel="nofollow" target="1">
   AWS Region Table
  </a>
 </p>
 <div class="Admonition_Note">
  <p>
   <span class="autonumber">
    Note:
   </span>
   It is recommend to use NFS for large deployments.
  </p>
 </div>
